    "en": {
      "title": "An SF soldier died after being attacked by a wild elephant",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A soldier was killed when he was attacked by a wild elephant while an Army team was engaged in a training exercise in the Valamandiya forest area in Aralaganwila.",
        "The deceased has been identified as a 19-year-old trainee of the Maduruoya Army Special Forces Training School.",
        "He was seriously injured in the attack and died after being admitted to Aralagangwila Hospital. A resident of Ambagasduwa area has lost his life. Aralagangwila police are conducting further investigations."
      ],
